Carragher: &quot;I can&rsquo;t get my head around it (#Mignolet dropped). Again it shows #Klopp still has a lack of confidence in both goalkeepers.&quot;<br />
<br />
#Carrager on #Mignolet being dropped from #LFCvArsenal: &quot;It's bizarre.&quot;

Klopp on Mignolet: &quot;He didn&rsquo;t want to rest, it&rsquo;s not a problem. We spoke yesterday about it and I really thought it made sense.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Especially because we have the quality in behind. It is just because I want to let him have a rest after this really intense time.&quot;
